Package homework2

Class BipartiteGraph<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • homework2.BipartiteGraph<T>

  • public class BipartiteGraph<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A BipartiteGraph is a graph that has two sets of vertexes - black and white. There are edges only between vertexes from different sets. T is the label of a vertex, T is a label of an edge.
